<div class="contextual-help-item principal-help"  i18n:domain="novaideo"
     tal:define="idea_to_support request.support_ideas">
     <p i18n:translate="" tal:condition="idea_to_support">The published ideas are visible by all members of the platform. They can either support or oppose them.</p>

    <span tal:omit-tag="" tal:condition="not idea_to_support">
        <p i18n:translate="">
           The published ideas are visible by all members of the platform.
        </p>
        <p i18n:translate="" >
            They can be transformed into proposals or used in existing proposals by members of the platform.
        </p>
    </span>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        The published ideas can also be duplicated. You can then work on the copy as you wish. You can also add published ideas to your favourites.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
        They can also be communicated to third parties or discussed among members.
    </p>
</div>